-- NRG Energy to Buy GenOn in Stock Purchase Valued at $1.7 Bln
-- B y   D a n   H a r t
-- 2012-07-22T18:19:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-22/nrg-energy-to-buy-genon-in-stock-purchase-valued-at-1-7-bln.html
NRG Energy Inc. (NRG)  plans to buy  GenOn
Energy Inc. (GEN)  in a stock transaction valued at $1.7 billion, the
companies said.  GenOn holders will receive 0.1216 of a share of NRG stock
for each share they hold, the companies said in a statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Hart at 
 dahart@bloomberg.net  